precis:
Authority for the Minister of Foreign Affairs (a) to sign a HEADQUARTERS
AGREEMENT between Canada and the SECRETARIAT OF THE CONVENTION ON
BIOLOGICAL DIVERSITY, or (b) to issue an Instrument of Full Powers
authorizing either the Hon. Sergio Marchi, the Hon. John A. Fraser or one
of several senior officials, to sign the Agreement on behalf of Canada.
